OL,3,C'If you can't afford to get your cat
OL,4,Cneutered, don't get one' warns charity
OL,6,FAn animal sanctuary in Oxfordshire
OL,7,Fsays the number of unwanted kittens
OL,8,Fhas doubled in the past two years,
OL,9,Fmainly because owners are not
OL,10,Fneutering their pets.
OL,12,FAnimal charities are becoming
OL,13,Foverwhelmed with unwanted kittens
OL,14,Fbecause people aren't neutering their
OL,15,Fcats.
OL,17,FThe RSPCA says more than 1,400 cats
OL,18,Fwere in its care across England and
OL,19,FWales at the end of 2025 - an increase
OL,20,Fof 72% from four years ago.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
