CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1779127867
OL,3,C'If you can't afford to get your cat
OL,4,Cneutered, don't get one' warns charity
OL,6,FIt's believed a lack of vet
OL,7,Fappointments and the rising cost of
OL,8,Fsurgery is to blame.
OL,10,FSpeaking to ITV News, manager of the
OL,11,FOxfordshire Animal Sanctuary, Iain
OL,12,FAtkin said they are seeing almost 200
OL,13,Fmore kittens every year arriving,
OL,14,Fneeding to be looked after.
OL,16,F"Mainly it's because people are not
OL,17,Fneutering their cats or there are lots
OL,18,Fof stray, un-neutered cats roaming
OL,19,Faround that are multiplying with lots
OL,20,Fand lots of numbers of kittens.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1779127867
OL,3,C'If you can't afford to get your cat
OL,4,Cneutered, don't get one' warns charity
OL,6,F"I would think it's partly cost of
OL,7,Fliving crisis, partly vet bills,
OL,8,Fpeople can't afford to neuter their
OL,9,Fcats.
OL,11,F"Now whilst I would agree that vet
OL,12,Fbills have gone up quite significantly
OL,13,Ffor all of us, I think the main point
OL,14,Fis if you can't afford to get your cat
OL,15,Fneutered, don't get one in the first
OL,16,Fplace."
OL,18,FCharities such as the RSPCA in
OL,19,FOxfordshire offer help the cost of
OL,20,Fneutering your pet.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
