PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1779127867
OL,3,C'If you can't afford to get your cat
OL,4,Cneutered, don't get one' warns charity
OL,6,FThe system runs on means-tested
OL,7,Fbenefits so that pets that are
OL,8,Fvulnerable to unwanted pregnancies can
OL,9,Fbe treated.
OL,11,FThose who qualify are offered a
OL,12,Fvoucher which is emailed to the vet,
OL,13,Fand deducted from the bill.
OL,15,FLocal vet Zoe Fry added that neutering
OL,16,Fcan be beneficial to cats' health.
OL,18,F"If you remove the parts, you remove
OL,19,Fthe risk of cancer in that particular
OL,20,Forgan," she said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1779127867
OL,3,C'If you can't afford to get your cat
OL,4,Cneutered, don't get one' warns charity
OL,6,F"We also enormously reduce the risk of
OL,7,Fsome communicable diseases like FIV,
OL,8,Fwhich is the cat version of AIDS, and
OL,9,Ffeline FELV as well. Those diseases
OL,10,Ftend to be spread by contact, either
OL,11,Fthrough mating or fighting.
OL,13,F"Both those behaviours are more or
OL,14,Fless eradicated, if not reduced, by
OL,15,Fneutering your animal before they go
OL,16,Foutside when they're young."
OL,18,FThe cost of neutering a cat can be
OL,19,Fbetween #100 and #250, but Zoe says
OL,20,Foften for female cats the price is
OL,21,Fheavily subsidised.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1779127867
OL,3,C'If you can't afford to get your cat
OL,4,Cneutered, don't get one' warns charity
OL,6,F"I'm very sympathetic to the cost now,
OL,7,Fand how prices for going to the vet
OL,8,Fhas increased an enormous amount
OL,9,Frecently.
OL,11,F"For a female cat, we are talking
OL,12,Fabout a sort of full ovarian
OL,13,Fhysterectomy - it is an invasive
OL,14,Fabdominal surgery.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
