OL,3,C'If you can't afford to get your cat
OL,4,Cneutered, don't get one' warns charity
OL,6,F"However, we can do it almost through
OL,7,Fa keyhole procedure when they're young
OL,8,Fand when they're small, and we can do
OL,9,Fit at a discounted price when it is
OL,10,Funcomplicated, when they are not
OL,11,Fpregnant, when they are not infected,
OL,12,Fand their recovery is really quick."
